➜罗红建(河南)：《纸上的江湖》
http://www.sohu.com/a/434281452_100115135	42650
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《纸上的江湖》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/罗红建(河南)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201125/0dd848c05c0e45cf8e74676fdb34fb8b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（一）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">半卷风高，半卷月黯……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玄机未露时，任由——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一杯弓影蛰伏，欲合隐张</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201125/e94efa17c25943efb996ae676c37abd2.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（二）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再落一笔，柔情便尽……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却是，不能抵挡刀光凭空</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">迟暮时——败兵，无处可逃</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
