➜广东诗人欧大象：游南海西樵拾零
http://www.sohu.com/a/434284438_100115135	43485
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>游南海西樵拾零(押平水韵一东. 五首)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/ 欧大象</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201125/521ce8a1742f42cbb617444637116b7a.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">南海观音</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一、</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">观音如坐九霄中,闭目凝神万念空。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日映祥云生五彩,灵光闪烁耀苍穹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201125/6f251c45134c4e8fb2b4fcf3dee5a036.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">西樵山天湖</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>二、</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">群山隐处有奇逢,谁抱天湖上半空。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧水深宵邀霁月,曦光照影入寒宫。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/eea3d5b677ec4705b4b5fb295527f9fe.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">西樵山白云洞</span></img></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>三、</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白云洞景互争雄,更有流溪锦鲤红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">骚客多情书满壁,不留方寸我吟枫。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201125/3d05b112726f4597b0fb9d270d736761.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">西樵山听音湖</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>四、</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寒英残柳苦凌风,渺渺烟波伴老翁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抛弃心头千个愿,听音湖畔笑长空。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201125/e9c20f2665d64a79ba4b5497b94b8939.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">黄飞鸿狮艺武术馆</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五、</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黄家师傅谓飞鸿,天下闻名好武功。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">独创一招无影脚,为民除暴大英雄。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201125/b1131586882f4f14b60fd0dbffff4c9d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong> 欧大象(又名：文光)，广东省阳春市人。现为阳江市、阳春市诗词楹联学会会员，广东省楹联学会会员，中华诗词学会会员，中国楹联学会会员。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201125/24f3e8a17657415098a0906f403a9504.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
