➜广西诗人陈熠明：丹霞日上秀长天
http://www.sohu.com/a/434287083_100115135	44224
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201125/2fbe643d4e2344969d1c01873cad0e5c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>丹霞日上秀长天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·红船引浪碧波来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蜿蜒岸上山龙到，荡漾江中水日开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">紫鹭接云黄鹤去，红船引浪碧波来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·江中有我浪情长</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天边紫鹤正飞翔，绚丽丹霞映水光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">望远别愁千里梦，江中有我浪情长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(三)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·心中美梦红平果</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大地山前观跃马，高天日上看飞鹰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心中美梦红平果，故里新潮碧友情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201125/aac2bdc94f9d4f0aa1879584ed4367fa.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
